entry.title: Protests Spread Across Iran Over Woman's Death in Police Detention
entry.content: Women removed their state-mandated headscarves in the streets to protest the death of a woman who was accused of violating the country’s Islamic dress code.

entry.title: Ukraine Forces Take Control of Key River Bank, Extending Advance in East
entry.content: Ukrainian forces said they now control the eastern bank of the Oskil River in the Kharkiv region, while Russia continues to launch attacks against civilian infrastructure in Ukraine following its military setbacks in the country’s east.
